  <string name="app_name">Textbender</string>

  <string name="accessibility_service_summary">
    Perform arbitrary actions on screen text.
  </string>

  <string name="accessibility_service_description">
    The Textbender accessibility service is required by both the text button
    overlay and Kiwi Browser Yomichan support. To use either of these features,
    please enable this service.\n\nThe text button overlay may be activated by
    either the accessibility shortcut or the floating button, after which all
    visible text on the screen will be turned into clickable buttons with
    configurable actions.\n\nIn addition to the above, enabling this feature
    also allows Textbender to open text directly in the Yomichan addon in Kiwi
    Browser if both are installed. Support for this is experimental. Please view
    Textbender’s README for more information.
  </string>

